  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "During the Noctis Aeterna, the oceanic hive world Tsadrekha holds an astropathic beacon bright enough to keep the warp-storm dark at bay. Strike-Captain Kassar and the Unsung, an Alpha Legion warband stranded since the Scouring, are sent to seize and corrupt it, but Kharn the Betrayer turns the mission into a many-sided siege. Imperial Fists, Sororitas, Guardsmen and a saint defend the prize while rival Chaos warbands crowd the battlefield. A twisty Alpha Legion infiltration novel where freedom depends on lying faster than every other killer in the dark.",
